{"TopicId":215901,"ForumId":120,"TopicTitle":"TRIM Reset Feature","CreatedByName":"Manosman","CreatedById":228087,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-25T18:06:19Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Manosman","CreatedById":228087,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-25T18:06:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor those that dont know, you can hold ALT\u002B W,A,S,D\u00A0 to trim a direction on a wing or gimbal.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nit would be nice to have a reset to zero feature,\u00A0 maybe ALT tap \u002B ALT hold for 2 seconds?\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nThoughts?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ravlain","CreatedById":201257,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-26T11:45:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlt-z resets trim.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Buzz313th","CreatedById":149043,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-27T04:29:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI thought it was alt x...\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ravlain","CreatedById":201257,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-27T07:31:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOops my bad, Alt-x is correct.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lyneira","CreatedById":149515,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-30T16:00:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt would, however, be nice if Alt-x didn\u0027t also cut your throttle... Quite annoying when flying (space)planes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"shdwlrd","CreatedById":113880,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-31T18:07:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis would be the better solution.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022113880\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed2680647637\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/213860-suggestion-separate-trim-keys-please/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:195px;max-width:500px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp